    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重拾熟悉的世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上一段旅程，回到你曾经熟知、如今却被黑暗笼罩的世界。用色彩泼洒前路，在无形的关卡中揭示方向，并在游玩过程中将其化为美丽的艺术作品。在揭开秘密的同时，逐步恢复这个梦幻国度被遗忘的光彩与美丽。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075240/extras/8e279e23b7c5da9d8357adb970f5a5be.poster.avif?t=1766135887\" width=798 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075240/extras/8e279e23b7c5da9d8357adb970f5a5be.webm?t=1766135887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075240/extras/8e279e23b7c5da9d8357adb970f5a5be.mp4?t=1766135887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >&lt;探索 · 解谜 · 战斗&gt;</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越超过 30 个令人费解的场景，解开谜题并迎战强大的首领。每一步都将你带向那神秘黑暗的源头。随着探索的深入，你将获得新的能力，带来多样化的绘画方式，并发现如万花筒般的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075240/extras/704c0f5ef5ba0a22a4d2e0f8dc121ead.poster.avif?t=1766135887\" width=798 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075240/extras/704c0f5ef5ba0a22a4d2e0f8dc121ead.webm?t=1766135887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075240/extras/704c0f5ef5ba0a22a4d2e0f8dc121ead.mp4?t=1766135887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重建平衡与光明</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在旅途中，你将与灵魂向导 Phoebe 并肩同行，她曾经认识你。通过在Finding Your Way里不断前进，将平衡、色彩与生命重新带回这个迷人的梦境世界。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075240/extras/16ec5c9cec80fa44c2a411e8bbe5bdf9.poster.avif?t=1766135887\" width=798 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075240/extras/16ec5c9cec80fa44c2a411e8bbe5bdf9.webm?t=1766135887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075240/extras/16ec5c9cec80fa44c2a411e8bbe5bdf9.mp4?t=1766135887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Finding Your Way</i> 是一款独特的游戏体验，由 Ben James 与《Kentucky Route Zero》的编剧 Jake Elliot 共同创作</p>",
